I want a peaceful life without complications.

24
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:50,240
What do you mean?

25
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:54,520
I just want to take care of my grandma. That's it.

26
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:59,380
So, stop messing with me. I know you're just fooling around.

27
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:01,050
I'm off.

28
