What's wrong with Chen Jian? I thought he wanted a divorce.

30
00:02:12,220 --> 00:02:18,280
He didn't cherish our relationship, but now he refuses to let go.

31
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,360
Forget about that loser.

32
00:02:21,340 --> 00:02:24,000
- Let me help you. 
 - No need.

33
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,480
- Be careful. 
 - You may break my arm. Don't.

34
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:28,040
Sorry.

35
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:30,260
My arm...

36
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:33,780
What would you like to eat, Jia Yu? Let me show off my cooking skills.

37
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:38,340
Please don't. I will never forget the dishes you made.

38
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:39,800
Let's just order takeout.

39
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:43,440
You've traumatized my son with your cooking.

40
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:46,880
Fine, it's my treat. Order it on my phone.

41
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,780
Thanks, Godmother.

42
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:56,340
What about the child if you get divorced?

43
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:59,320
I don't care about anything else. Jia Yu is my whole world.

44
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:02,060
Chen Jian can't take him away.

45
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:04,980
Let's get crab roe noodles again, okay?

46
00:03:04,980 --> 00:03:06,780
Okay.

47
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:09,960
No scallion for Godmother. Double scallion for Mom, right?

48
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,560
That's right.

49
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:37,120
 Here is Li Jin Yu's phone number. 

50
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:40,500
 Sister, this is all I can do for you. 

51
